<i>noun</i>: 흉포 [흉포], 포학 [포ː학], 참극 [참극], 잔학 [잔학], 잔악 [자낙], 만행 [만행], 극악 [그각] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>흉포 [흉포]</dt><br>
<dd>brutality; atrocity; ferocity</dd><br>
<dd>성질이 매우 흉악하고 포악함.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of one's personality being brutal and violent.</dd><br>
<dt>포학 [포ː학]</dt><br>
<dd>tyranny; atrocity</dd><br>
<dd>성질이나 행동이 몹시 잔인하고 난폭함.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of one’s personality or behavior being very cruel and fierce.</dd><br>
<dt>참극 [참극]</dt><br>
<dd>tragedy; disaster; atrocity</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 슬프고 끔찍한 일.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) A sad and awful occurrence.</dd><br>
<dt>잔학 [잔학]</dt><br>
<dd>cruelty; brutality; atrocity</dd><br>
<dd>인정 없이 매우 잔인하고 사나움.</dd><br>
<dd>The quality of being very cruel and ferocious without mercy.</dd><br>
<dt>잔악 [자낙]</dt><br>
<dd>cruelty; brutality; atrocity</dd><br>
<dd>인정이 없고 아주 모질며 악독함.</dd><br>
<dd>The quality of being merciless, very cruel, and brutal.</dd><br>
<dt>만행 [만행]</dt><br>
<dd>atrocity; brutality</dd><br>
<dd>잔인하고 야만적인 행위.</dd><br>
<dd>A cruel and brutal act.</dd><br>
<dt>극악 [그각]</dt><br>
<dd>atrocity; viciousness; flagrant cruelty</dd><br>
<dd>더할 나위 없이 악하고 독함.</dd><br>
<dd>Being incomparably evil and spiteful.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>